Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to die on your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let go of the RED Strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no mission this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you go out with me?\NThere's a place I want to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Baki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A crime in reality♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪For Heaven's sake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Accepts any fake♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Won't take it at all, I get sick♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪A girl looking back♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:02:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Casts the miracle into this instant world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Did you lie♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Spit the venom♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I know why♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've found a game of ecstasy♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Red Criminal gets life♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've never been in love♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Don't know when I started getting sick of this world♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♪We will fly♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Someday I won't be crying♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I've been sacrificing myself not to hurt anybody♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET GUARDIANS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Up next, we have Other attack forecast\Nfor each province.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The probability for Suoh Capital is 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,For Seiran, it's 15%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The probability for Togetsu is 12%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"OTHERS TODAY"\NThe Extinction Belt is at the stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is currently no impact on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a higher chance of it\Napproaching certain areas in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-I think the person who saved me was Kasane.\N-Please stay cautious at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But members of OSF might have stunted growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.\NAppearances can be deceptive in OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Lieutenant Arashi Spring\Nis the elder sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki is\Nthe younger brother instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The age and the appearances\Nhave no direct relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is basically no need\Nfor honorific titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore the ranks and titles,\Nwhat matters is true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Seto said so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Kasane and Naomi are both\Namateurs just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They are only 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Naomi is the elder sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to take up your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let you go out alone,\Nyou might attract creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us have powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to our powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot only access psynet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but also use it for many things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,such as shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,PAYMENT COMPLETED
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can search for information\Nand send messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us have power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they are the OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarlet Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved mankind from total annihilation\Nwith the Spring of Extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the founding father of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A great man indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ancestor's grave is now\Na tourism destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born over 2000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't feel any relation in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,BAKI TALISMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An omikuji event in collaboration with Baki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the founding father is fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi and Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here for the omikuji too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here with Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask Kasane to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, do you like Baki too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well...\N-Now that we are here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have some tea after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still some time before\Nour mission this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, beware of this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I should have come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did I do something wrong?\N-Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, Naomi, do you have a sister\Nthat is much older than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is my only sibling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any relatives\Nwho joined OSF in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's draw the omikuji now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have some tea together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"GREAT DISASTER"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, what did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone got the worst omikuji ever\Nexcept for Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At least not all of us will get bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have an OSF mission afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a buzzkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Give it to me.\N-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito and Nagi, give me yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This should turn your bad luck\Ninto lesser good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it our best from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so gentle and kind, Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your kindness saved us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me too! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seiran front?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an abandoned underground railway line,\Nit's near the Suoh Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they are going in to investigate\Nthe Other activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They refuse to heed our advice\Ndespite the objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Send in backups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's another report
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we have yet to verify.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some suspicious activities in Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon is stirring up troubles again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will report after the investigation\Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yuito doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the report of him defeating an Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get a chance to talk to him\Nafter he joined the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he is my brother, but I can't give him\Nany special treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for the report today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I should leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seirans are on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The joint beginner training of\NSeto Platoon and Kyoka Platoon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A joint training?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The rule is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 5v5 simulation battle\Nbetween Seto Platoon and Kyoka Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The first team to secure\Nthe flag in the middle wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only four in Kyoka Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems different from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When we saw her online and on the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give it my best too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when she's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What we see here is her usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People in the OSF call her Lazy Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, let's get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the proof of our bond as sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sister.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you concerned about Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, what made you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not particularly concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just find him a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he is qualified to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will find it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"MAJOR SHIDEN RITTER, POWER: ELECTROKINESIS"\NYoung Master of the Sumeragi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"CAPTAIN GEMMA GARRISON"\NHe defeated an Other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"POWER: SCLEROKINESIS"\N on his first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down around him, Shiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"HARUKA FRAZER, POWER: TELEPATHY"\NIt's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"MAJOR KYOKA EDEN, POWER: DUPLICATION"\NGo for it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same trick as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My power is clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can foresee the future in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too lazy to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Gemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You could sense me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull any punches, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I must get the flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, don't you remember the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,FAILURE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,VICTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be enough for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She is quite a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not too shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the same when we last fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it takes more to earn my acknowledgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you deserve my sister or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean about observing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on making it into the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still against the idea of you joining OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least don't get yourself hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're a member of OSF now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that means you can hold your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to use this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to talk to you about our family\Nand your late mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have dinner with Kaito another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero, your surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you hated training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have new members every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention there are more girls\Njoining our platoon this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make sure they see\Nthe awesome side of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Deployment order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Other activities confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The location is the abandoned railway line\Nof Suoh Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto Platoon and Kyoka Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,please deploy immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of them fell from the Extinction Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others have got in through\Nthe air vents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication devices might be affected here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Relying solely on telepathy without brain talk
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,will result in a one-way communication from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's pray the comms will work fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seto Platoon, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Platoon, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The past and future of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin the attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, the communication disruption caused\Nby the Extinction Belt is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. How is Kyoka Platoon doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies from above, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Haruka, repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are attacking from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, Shiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kasane and Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, Naomi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, where are Captain Seto and the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost communication with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know they will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Kyoka and the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They can handle this level of enemies with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Nagi!\N-Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemma, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all right. What about the other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Nagi and Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them. They are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the other side of these boulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. They are surrounded by Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect the SAS cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move, Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I don't need to let fate dictate me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Because I believe that I can rewrite it♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪What's waiting for us at the world's end♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal, keep the fire going♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can shake us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Who can define us♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪It's nothing less than our story♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.21,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CONSPIRACY
